"Time Limit
-- The Human Auction Begins"

55
00:03:51,890 --> 00:03:54,210
"Navy Headquarters"

56
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:03,760
"Dark King" Silvers Rayleigh, huh...

57
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:06,730
Apparently, no one around him
recognizes him,

58
00:04:06,730 --> 00:04:09,600
so he's being sold
as a regular old man...

59
00:04:13,410 --> 00:04:16,480
The Dark King,
being sold at a human auction?

60
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,800
It is hard to believe something like this
would happen to the real one.

61
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:25,640
My men aren't 100% sure
it's really him, either...

62
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:26,230
Tea!

63
00:04:26,230 --> 00:04:27,280
Oh, thank you.

64
00:04:28,130 --> 00:04:29,920
What should we do, Vice-Admiral?

65
